Title: An Automated Approach to Evaluating Dose-Effect Experiments
        Following Litchfield and Wilcoxon (1949)
Authors@R: person(given="Jean V.", family="Adams",
        email="jvadams@usgs.gov", role=c("aut", "cre"))
